text: "Baby I" is the 2nd single from Ariana Grande debut studio album Yours Truly. It went to number 21 in the United States, number 6 in Japan, number 67 in Australia, number 57 in Canada and number 39 in the Netherlands. ==References== Category:2013 songs Category:Pop songs Category:R&B; songs Category:Ariana Grande songs
title: Baby I
